name.description:
The name (project, location, cluster id) of the cluster to set networking
policy. Specified in the format 'projects/*/locations/*/clusters/*'.

networkPolicy.description: Configuration options for the NetworkPolicy feature.

enabled.description: Whether network policy is enabled on the cluster.
